{"tid":1132481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<<有圖>>【內臟糞便齊流】由剖腹產疤痕爆出 腸炎媽要同時換5器官保命","createTime":"2019-04-30T10:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T18:54:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c23ac8c95ae66aa4bc3503d43e84177dc073e6f3","tid":1132481,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"英國一名患有慢性腸炎的女子腹部出現瘺孔，更試過多個內臟連同血水及糞便，由爆開的剖腹產疤痕間漏出，相當恐怖。她不敢開懷進食，後來病情惡化，要同時接受肝臟、胰臟、大小腸等共5器官的移植手術，有報道形容是「世上難度最高的手術」。<br />\n來自打比郡（Derbys）的43歲奧迪（Michelle Oddy），在14歲時確診患上無法根治的克隆氏症（Crohn's disease）。患者會嚴重腹瀉、腹痛、排便次數不規律，亦可產生瘺孔，即潰瘍蝕穿腸道，形成孔洞蝕入鄰近器官。<br />\n奧迪稱腹部在2014年發生過一場「爆炸」，「有天早上我一起身發現腹部爆開了，漏出血液和糞便，我的內臟都跌出來，全身都是血。我只想好好進食、外出，不想繼續擔心腹部會爆開並漏出內臟。」2015年她的體重急降至只有25公斤，「他們說我的內臟全都出問題，我只有數天壽命。」<br />\n奧迪後來接受「全胃腸外營養」治療（Total Parenteral Nutrition／TPN），即從靜脈輸入營養液成功續命，4星期後可以出院。但自始她要依賴「TPN」和造口袋，直到2018年她因昏迷再度入院，當時病情危殆，醫生認為她的肝臟、胰臟、小腸、大腸和半個胃共5個器官已喪失功能，全部都要更換。<br />\n一次過移植多個器官的手術需時20小時，既複雜而且高風險，只有約40%成功機會，劍橋艾登布魯克斯醫院（Addenbrooke'sHospital）安排奧迪在下月接受手術，接受來自同一位捐贈者的5個器官移植。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190430/large/1556605641_f47a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190430%2Flarge%2F1556605641_f47a.jpg&h=62aca6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190430/59546109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190430%2F59546109&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1f3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=f70b35b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190430%2F59546109&h=819a6972\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190430/59546109</a>"},{"pid":"3740bc12719e31a9a3e766172d679248a3bd68d7","tid":1132481,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190430/large/1556604458_540b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190430%2Flarge%2F1556604458_540b.jpg&h=756abc24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b320910766e7184379cdec1c0af2d91dcf6cac9c","tid":1132481,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"高清大圖"},{"pid":"3de07c7a0b7e00119b9a8b2669f7ea0cdfcd827b","tid":1132481,"uid":251086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"呢d唔使講都知有圖"},{"pid":"06aeb7e28c22c994bc6217bb45ae40b09ec60a38","tid":1132481,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"呢d就有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f930061ec4c7d6c54f93ee53a0b3cee7a948697f","tid":1132481,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de07c7a0b7e00119b9a8b2669f7ea0cdfcd827b","tid":1132481,"uid":251086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"呢d唔使講都知有圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabc315d6465e88976c5aa4652ddb3692e6a7f16","tid":1132481,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"唔知佢有冇一路打字一路撿返d腸呀內臟呀腎呀呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d14e8b5732d6d2c1dc04cc9d83ded5534f4b90c","tid":1132481,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:54:04.000Z","msg":"咪做大Sai鬼"}]}